202
00:12:15.740 --> 00:12:16.560
Kumohon.

203
00:12:17.940 --> 00:12:19.370
Tidak akan kuberi tahu.

204
00:12:19.870 --> 00:12:21.160
Paman Song.

205
00:12:21.340 --> 00:12:23.890
Yuanwei. Coba kau pikir lagi.

206
00:12:24.510 --> 00:12:26.400
Kenapa dia terus mendekatimu?

207
00:12:26.750 --> 00:12:27.520
