213
00:12:45.940 --> 00:12:46.610
Nona, makan mi-nya.

214
00:12:46.630 --> 00:12:47.490
Cepat makan.

215
00:12:48.150 --> 00:12:48.850
Enak.

216
00:12:49.180 --> 00:12:53.090
