549
00:38:17.190 --> 00:38:18.590
Dewi Hua.

550
00:38:18.590 --> 00:38:20.710
Aku datang memohon perjodohan.

551
00:38:20.710 --> 00:38:24.210
Semoga bisa bertemu pria idaman
yang berwajah tampan, gagah,

552
00:38:24.230 --> 00:38:24.940
dan baik kepadaku.

553
00:38:24.940 --> 00:38:27.210
Pokoknya jangan seperti Pei Jihuai.

554
00:38:27.380 --> 00:38:28.600
Kumohon.

555
00:38:30.860 --> 00:38:31.600
Di sini.

556
00:38:31.630 --> 00:38:34.040
Kuil Dewi Hua sangat manjur,
kita bisa memohon apa saja

557
00:38:34.040 --> 00:38:35.340
